<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Mba ampio, ry Tompo soa FFPM278</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mba ampio, ry Tompo soa
 Izahay navotanao,
 Fa mikasa mba hanoa
 Sy hanaraka Anao ;
 Hitanao fa kely hery
 Izahay mpanomponao,
 Tsy mahefa raha irery,
 Koa mba tarihonao.

[V2]
 Izahay manolo-tena
 Mba hiasa ho Anao,
 Ka maniry, manantena
 Fa hanampy Hianao ;
 Hitanao fa kely hery, ..sns.

[V3]
 Tianay hiara-dia
 Aminao, ry Tomponay,
 Ka tantano tsy hania
 Amin'ny alehanay.
 Hitanao fa kely hery, ..sns.</lyrics>
<author>A.R. Randrianantenaina</author>
<hymn_number>278</hymn_number>
</song>